iana and Kentucky?  I was interested in volunteering to help with cleanup.  ',0,'2012-03-05 13:45:09','2012-03-05 13:45:09'),(319,293,'Newsletter Signup From New Account',0,'2012-03-05 13:51:25','2012-03-05 13:51:25'),(320,294,'Newsletter Signup Form Submittal',0,'2012-03-05 14:36:37','2012-03-05 14:36:37'),(321,295,' Hello, I\'m very fasinated with your disaster relief. I think it\'s wonderful and amzing thay you guys would take all your time and effort to meet the needs of those poor people. I really want to start fundraisers to support that area, especially if you guys could use those funds in the midwest that just had all those tornados. I think its just horrible and sad what happened and I want to help as much as I can even though I\'m only 15. I have some people who are willing to help with these fundraisers such as a yardsale, bakesale, dinners, cleaning and maybe more. Please pray that these will work and that God would touch the hearts of the american people. I\'ve felt a calling to do something for quite some time and I feel like God gave me the courage to finally speak up. I hope you don\'t mind if the checks come through the mail instead of a credit card. It would just work better that way. Now I make no promises if it will be a lot or if I\'ll get any money for you. I just hope that God will bless this as he has blessed you.      Your friend in faith, Elizabeth',0,'2012-03-05 18:36:26','2012-03-05 18:36:26'),(322,296,'Newsletter Signup Form Submittal',0,'2012-03-05 19:27:25','2012-03-05 19:27:25'),(323,297,'Newsletter Signup From New Account',0,'2012-03-05 19:45:08','2012-03-05 19:45:08'),(324,298,'Hello, I\'m writing in regards to your program \"water for the world\". I\'m interested in maybe finding out the company you use for the drilling process. If able it would be a blessing. if not, could you refer me to known drillers that could help our cause. thank you and God bless.\r\nDaniel Zahm\r\nAmbassador @ iGiveH2ope.org ',0,'2012-03-05 21:14:26','2012