centage of the daily sales to your charity. \r\n\r\n2)	Featured Deal – We showcase your organization as its own featured deal and let our customers donate directly to your charity. With this, we would design an offer that tells others about your charity’s mission and then we present a donation option to the user.   You would write a blurb about what your organization would do with the funds so others can understand the good that will come from their donation.  We collect an advertising fee with this method.\r\n\r\nWhat’s in it for us?  Shoppers buy more when they feel a percentage of the sales will go towards a charity.  What’s in it for you?  You receive a large donation check derived from a percentage of our deal revenues.\r\n\r\nWorking with us is easy.  If you chose option 1, we just need a logo and mission statement sent to us via email and we will send your donation check 30 days after the deal is concluded.  If you chose option 2, you would send us a logo, main graphic, mission statement, organization profile and a use of funds statement.    Your donation check will arrive within 70 days (10 days after the 60 day customer return policy has elapsed.)\r\n\r\nIf you are interested, please contact us at 512-777-4480 or respond by email diana@dealfanatic.com if you would like to discuss further.\r\n\r\nThanks,\r\nDiana.\r\n',0,'2012-03-14 20:01:13','2012-03-14 20:01:13'),(352,329,'Newsletter Signup From New Account',0,'2012-03-14 20:51:19','2012-03-14 20:51:19'),(353,330,'Dear Sirs:\r\n\r\nI was referred to you website by a blog in reference to grants. I have viewed your site, but I am not sure if you can be of any help to us. We are a four year old church plant whose demographic is reaching unchurched and non christian teenagers. From our research, we cannot find another church like us in the US. We are not just a youth ministry.\r\n\r\nWhile we have a small number of adults in our core, we are not able to keep up with the growth of the ministry from a financial 