Jesus Christ.\r\nThen the Lord gave me a burden in 2006 to start ministry called \"BETHEL HARVEST MINISTRIES\" we are working in the slums in Chennaseri\r\nand we having church planting,Evangelism, and tract distribution, personal evangelism, crusades,seminar, children ministry, widow\'s ministry and helping poor. Please\r\npray for our ministry. Praise God now we have 13 small house churches and each church we have 30-40 new believers, One who converted from Idol\r\nWorship .And we have 12 full time workers and 24 volunteers are working.So I am looking some prayer support and spiritual cover and your great financial support , I like your fellowship. If god allows we will do together great thing for lord in india. if you wish please be a prayer partner to this ministry in India. And also please visit our ministry link page www.bethelharvest.weebly.com\r\n\r\n\r\nYour Brother In Christ,\r\nA.V.DICROSE',0,'2012-04-03 05:42:03','2012-04-03 05:42:03'),(415,384,'Kenneth R & Marlene Eash\r\n\r\nhave moved from the address of\r\n\r\n8771 N 700W, Ligonier, IN 46767\r\n\r\nseven years ago.  Please remove this\r\n\r\naddress from your mailing lists.',0,'2012-04-03 14:17:54','2012-04-03 14:17:54'),(416,385,'Are you able to receive donations of prescription medications?',0,'2012-04-03 16:02:00','2012-04-03 16:02:00'),(417,386,'Newsletter Signup Form Submittal',0,'2012-04-04 08:51:21','2012-04-04 08:51:21'),(418,387,'Newsletter Signup From New Account',0,'2012-04-04 20:33:41','2012-04-04 20:33:41'),(419,388,'Hello,\r\nMy name is Angela Mitchell and I am in search of grants/charitable funds to help purchase a newer, more feasible handicap accessible van for my mother-in-law. \r\nApproximately 10 years ago the doctors found a tumor in her spine. After spending time at the Mayo clinic and having the tumor removed she had little feeling in her legs which has over the years gotten progressively worse. She currently owns a handicap accessible van, but has to manipulate herself into it